params.name: filepath
params.description: the path of file to construct vocabulary.

params.name: unk_token
params.description: special token for unknown token. If noneed, it also could be None. Default: None.

params.name: pad_token
params.description: special token for padding token. If noneed, it also could be None. Default: None.

params.name: bos_token
params.description: special token for bos token. If no need,it also could be None. Default: None.

params.name: eos_token
params.description: special token for eos token. If no need,it also could be None. Default: None.

params.name: kwargs
params.description: Keyword arguments ending with _token. It can beused to specify further special tokens that will be exposed asattribute of the vocabulary and associated with an index.

return.description: An instance of Vocab generated from the given file.
